@page "/pricing"
<h1>Pricing</h1>
<p>PrTask is completely free for everyone. No hidden fees, no commissions, no charges.</p>
<section class="pricing-cards">
    <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>For Developers</h3>
        <div class="pricing-amount">Free</div>
        <ul>
            <li>Browse and claim tasks at no cost</li>
            <li>Receive 100% of the bounty on each completed PR</li>
            <li>Earn XP, badges, and leaderboard rank</li>
            <li>Track your earnings and payout history</li>
            <li>Get paid via your preferred payout method</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing-card featured">
        <h3>For Clients</h3>
        <div class="pricing-amount">Free</div>
        <ul>
            <li>Post unlimited tasks with custom bounties</li>
            <li>Minimum bounty: $1</li>
            <li>Automatic payment on PR approval</li>
            <li>Pay via credit card or supported payment method</li>
            <li>Review and approve PRs before payout</li>
            <li>Dispute resolution and arbitration support</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="pricing-faq">
    <h2>Payment Details</h2>
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>How are payments processed?</h4>
        <p>When a client approves a pull request, they are automatically charged the bounty amount via their payment method. The developer receives 100% of the bounty.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>When do I get paid?</h4>
        <p>Payment is processed automatically when your PR is approved by the client. Developers receive 100% of the bounty via their preferred payout method.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>What currencies are supported?</h4>
        <p>All transactions are in US Dollars (USD).</p>
    </div>
</section>
